trans-unit.source: Contains the data sent to a tracking service by the runtime tracking infrastructure when a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint"></xref> is matched.
trans-unit.target: Contém os dados enviados para um serviço de controlo a infraestrutura de controlo do tempo de execução quando um <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint"> </xref> é correspondido.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] When the runtime tracking infrastructure matches a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> in a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>, it sends a UserTrackingRecord to the tracking service over the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel> associated with that tracking service.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Quando a infraestrutura de controlo do tempo de execução corresponde a um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>num <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>, envia um UserTrackingRecord para o serviço de controlo sobre o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel>associados a esse serviço de controlo.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: The tracking service can perform whatever action is required on the data in the tracking record.
trans-unit.target: O serviço de controlo pode efetuar qualquer ação é necessária nos dados no registo de controlo.

trans-unit.source: This constructor is called by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Este construtor é chamado pelo tempo de execução do controlo de infraestrutura.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord"></xref> class by using the specified parameters.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord"> </xref> classe utilizando os parâmetros especificados.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> of the activity associated with the user event.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Type>da atividade associada o eventos de utilizador.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.QualifiedName%2A?displayProperty=fullName> of the activity associated with the user event.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.QualifiedName%2A?displayProperty=fullName> da atividade associada o eventos de utilizador.

trans-unit.source: A number that identifies the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext"></xref> of the activity associated with the user event.
trans-unit.target: Um número que identifica o <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext"> </xref> da atividade associada o eventos de utilizador.

trans-unit.source: A number that identifies the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext"></xref> of the parent activity of the activity associated with the user event.
trans-unit.target: Um número que identifica o <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext"> </xref> da atividade principal da atividade associada o eventos de utilizador.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.DateTime> that indicates the date and time of the user event associated with the tracking record.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.DateTime>que indica a data e hora do evento associado o registo de controlo de utilizador.</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: The relative order in which the user event associated with this tracking record occurred in the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: A ordem relativa na qual o evento de utilizador associado a este registo de controlo ocorreu na instância de fluxo de trabalho.

trans-unit.source: A key associated with the user data for this tracking record, or a null reference (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""></xref> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: Uma chave associada com os dados de utilizador para este registo de controlo, ou uma referência nula (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""> </xref> no Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: The user data associated with the user event.
trans-unit.target: Os dados de utilizador associados o eventos de utilizador.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the common language runtime (CLR) type of the activity that emitted the user data for which this <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord"></xref> was created.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o tipo de runtime (CLR) de idioma comum de atividade que emitidos os dados de utilizador em que esta <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord"> </xref> foi criado.

trans-unit.source: This property is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Esta propriedade é definida pelo runtime infraestrutura de controlo.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> of the activity that emitted the user data.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Type>da atividade que emitidos os dados do utilizador.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of annotations associated with the user event.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a coleção de anotações associado o eventos de utilizador.

trans-unit.source: You can specify annotations to be associated with a user event in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Annotations%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Pode especificar anotações estar associado um evento de utilizador no <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Annotations%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Annotations%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: When the runtime tracking infrastructure matches the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>, it returns these annotations in Annotations.
trans-unit.target: Quando a infraestrutura de controlo do tempo de execução corresponde a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>, devolve estas anotações em anotações.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: This property is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Esta propriedade é definida pelo runtime infraestrutura de controlo.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"></xref> that contains the annotations that are associated with the user event by the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint"></xref> that was matched in the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"> </xref> que contém as anotações que estão associadas com o evento de utilizador pelo <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint"> </xref> foi correspondentes no <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a list containing any additional data extracted from the workflow for the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint"></xref> that was matched.
trans-unit.target: Obtém uma lista que contém quaisquer dados adicionais extraídos de fluxo de trabalho para o <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint"> </xref> foi correspondentes.

trans-unit.source: When a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> is matched, the runtime tracking infrastructure can extract data from the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Quando um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>é correspondido, tempo de execução do controlo de infraestrutura pode extrair dados da instância de fluxo de trabalho.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: The data to be extracted is specified by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Os dados a ser extraído são especificados por <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName> can contain <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> objects, which specify member data to be extracted from the activity associated with the user event, and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> objects, which specify member data to be extracted from the root activity of the workflow.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>pode conter <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>objetos que especificar dados do membro a ser extraído da atividade associada o eventos de utilizador, e <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>objetos que especificar membro de dados a ser extraído da atividade raiz do fluxo de trabalho.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract></xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Each type of extract can also specify annotations to be returned with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Cada tipo de extração também pode especificar anotações devem ser devolvidos com os dados extraídos.

trans-unit.source: The runtime tracking infrastructure encapsulates each piece of extracted data and its associated annotations in a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem> which it adds to Body.
trans-unit.target: A infraestrutura de controlo do tempo de execução encapsula cada peça de dados extraídos e respetivos anotações associadas num <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>que adiciona ao corpo.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>

trans-unit.source: Because the user data pushed to the tracking service by the user event is contained in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.UserData%2A>, Body will frequently be an empty list.
trans-unit.target: Porque os dados de utilizador enviado para o serviço de controlo pelo evento utilizador faz <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.UserData%2A>, corpo frequentemente será uma lista vazia.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.UserData%2A>

trans-unit.source: This property is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Esta propriedade é definida pelo runtime infraestrutura de controlo.

trans-unit.source: A list of <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"></xref> objects each of which contains a single piece of extracted data and its associated annotations.
trans-unit.target: Uma lista de <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"> </xref> objetos, cada um dos quais contém um único conjunto de dados extraídos e respetivos anotações associadas.

trans-unit.target: Contexto da atividade.

trans-unit.target: Um número que identifica o contexto da atividade.

trans-unit.source: Always a null reference (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""></xref> in Visual Basic) for a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Sempre uma referência nula (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""> </xref> no Visual Basic) para um <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: There is no event data associated with a user event, therefore, EventArgs has no meaning and is always a null reference (`Nothing`).
trans-unit.target: Não existem dados de eventos associados a um evento de utilizador, por conseguinte, EventArgs não tem nenhum significado e sempre uma referência nula (`Nothing`).

trans-unit.source: The user data that is pushed to the runtime tracking infrastructure by whichever one of the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.TrackData%2A> or <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext.TrackData%2A> methods that caused the user event is sent in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.UserData%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Os dados de utilizador que são enviados para o tempo de execução controlo infraestrutura por qualquer um dos <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.TrackData%2A>ou <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext.TrackData%2A>métodos que causou o evento de utilizador é enviada numa <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.UserData%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.UserData%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext.TrackData%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.TrackData%2A>

trans-unit.source: Any data extracts that are associated with the user event by the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> are encapsulated in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem> objects and sent in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Extrai os dados que está associados com o evento de utilizador por <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>são encapsulada em <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>objetos de e enviadas em <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>

trans-unit.target: Uma referência nula (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""></xref>) para um <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates the order of the user event that matched the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint"></xref> in the workflow instance.

trans-unit.source: EventOrder indicates the order of the user event that matched the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> relative to the other tracking events emitted by the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: EventOrder indica a ordem do evento de utilizador correspondentes a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>relativos os eventos de controlo emitidos pela instância do fluxo de trabalho.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: EventOrder will be unique within a workflow instance, but it is not guaranteed to be sequential.
trans-unit.target: EventOrder será exclusivo dentro de uma instância de fluxo de trabalho, mas não é garantido ser sequenciais.
